{"tid":1795941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 忙於巡演仍不忘行善　捐款幫助隔代教養家庭！","createTime":"2019-12-24T09:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:00:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f63fcbe657c56d7bf632ca1d3a47ff5daf320dd1","tid":1795941,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"在耶誕節前夕，一向熱心公益的 IU 再度為有需要的人們雪中送炭，光是這個消息便讓人覺得心頭溫暖！<br />\n<br />\n綠色雨傘兒童基金會最近透露，IU 捐獻了一億韓元，並拜託基金會將這筆款項用於資助隔代教養家庭中的孩子們。<br />\n<br />\nIU 自從 2015 年開始便持續透過綠色雨傘兒童基金會捐款，過去曾幫助過單親家庭、隔代教養家庭等等弱勢族群，在江原道發生山林大火時，也為當地兒童助一臂之力，今年 9 月時更以粉絲 Uaena 的名義捐款一億韓元，來慶祝自己出道滿十一週年！"},{"pid":"d7c5306a2649b78b59d53f61dd0028bafd1bbf80","tid":1795941,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/569ee5b177fd8e5eb8ac60103835e9ce/a01546e391d979f7-6e/s250x400/3fb26b54b65b77e6b8d0910c9ac07d2e62887c1f.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F569ee5b177fd8e5eb8ac60103835e9ce%2Fa01546e391d979f7-6e%2Fs250x400%2F3fb26b54b65b77e6b8d0910c9ac07d2e62887c1f.gifv&h=bcc40dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6a23c76f916f9a02f2ee0d69adbdd486/a01546e391d979f7-7f/s250x400/e546aba963fbcdd61bc58402b3ac913ef28e4e44.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6a23c76f916f9a02f2ee0d69adbdd486%2Fa01546e391d979f7-7f%2Fs250x400%2Fe546aba963fbcdd61bc58402b3ac913ef28e4e44.gifv&h=f887b48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/01be5b0778715f3615a11f469477181c/a01546e391d979f7-3a/s250x400/f6608d5296483af0fba772951a59f7b2934eafc8.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F01be5b0778715f3615a11f469477181c%2Fa01546e391d979f7-3a%2Fs250x400%2Ff6608d5296483af0fba772951a59f7b2934eafc8.gifv&h=f9c1f195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人美心善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\